    x^2=\sin^2(\alpha)=\frac{1}{2}(1-\cos(2\alpha)) 
   \Phi(\alpha)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}\sigma}e^{-\frac{1}{4\sigma^2}(1-\cos(2\alpha))}. 
